msgstr "số nguyên"

#: ../../whatsnew/3.0.rst:209
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
":pep:`237`: Essentially, :class:`!long` renamed to :class:`int`. That is, "
"there is only one built-in integral type, named :class:`int`; but it behaves"
